{"tid":1623040,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【召喚】黃藍商店list maker","createTime":"2019-10-04T18:08:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T18:08:00.000Z","uid":262465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"98db3ca784ac42aceb303328ff0d2b7a50f7feba","tid":1623040,"uid":262465,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T18:08:00.000Z","msg":"事緣小妹有好多唔識中文嘅frd子都想幫襯黃店<br />\n但！係！暫時所有嘅list/chatbot都係得中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />亦都好似無咩plan要整英文版<br />\n所以小妹想幫手整個英文版等多啲人可以用到，暫時最簡單快手做到係openrice個list (hker2019嗰個) ，跟住就係tg chatbot (@ybshopbot) <br />\n本身諗住搵佢地個admin傾，但我搵極都搵唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所以想喺度呢兩個list嘅主人講：<br />\n我可以幫手做英文版<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n快啲嚟搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">如果已經有英文版，唔好意思我柒咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />可唔可以share俾我等我啲frd有得用</span>"}]}